{
  "text": "The resulting second order structure function is shown in the right panel of Figure ( 3), with the longitudinal structure function of [CITATION_1] indicated by the dotted curve. The dashed line indicates twice the total energy. The two curves agree well, except at the smallest scales where the predicted S 2l is less than the observed. This may reflect deviations from isotropy and/or 2D non-divergence at small scales [e.g . 29] . Nevertheless the overall agreement is good.",
